title: North American Custom Covers Laser Dinghy Sailboat Deck Cover - Tailored, Waterproof & Breathable - Grey
features: Completely custom-fitted for the International Laser Class sailboat; also called Laser Standard and the Laser One
Grey colored 600 denier PU coated polyester material; UV protection
description: This cover is designed for the International Laser Class sailboat, also called Laser Standard and the Laser One. It has the Laser Standard Hull design, so is NOT compatible with the Laser 2. Our tailored dinghy covers are manufactured from 600 denier PU coated polyester, they are totally breathable, waterproof and treated to prevent UV damage, all stitching is UV protected for longevity. Spares and sails can be stored in the boat whilst the cover is on. There is a hole for the bow eye. We have added adjustable hull straps for complete security when storing your dinghy or towing.
